high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the candle on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn around and take two steps, turn right for four steps and stop in front of the sink cabinet.
Open the second cabinet door from the left and put the candle vertically at the front, center of the cabinet and shut the door.
Turn left for three steps and turn right to face the toilet.
Pick up the candle to the right of the green spray bottle on top of the toilet tank.
Turn right for four steps, then turn in a circle facing the sink cabinet.
Open the second cabinet door from the left and put the candle to the right of the first candle in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles in a cabinet underneath the sink.

Turn right and face the counter next to the sink in front of you.
Take the candle from the sink in front of you.
Turn left and face the cabinets to your right.
Place the candle in the cabinet under the sink in front of you and close it.

Take the candle on top of the toilet in front of you.
